Bragg Capital Trust - Queens Road Small Cap Value Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 4:48 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Bragg Capital Trust - Queens Road Small Cap Value Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bragg Capital Trust - Queens Road Small Cap Value Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Bragg Financial Advisors, Inc. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in value stocks of small-cap companies having market capitalization less than that of the company with the largest capitalization included in the Russell 2000 Value Index. The fund employs fundamental analysis by focusing on factors such as discounted price-to-earnings (P/E) and price-to-cash flow (P/CF) multiples, strong balance sheets, and have experienced management to create its portfolio. It ben...
Bragg Capital Trust - Queens Road Small Cap Value Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Bragg Financial Advisors, Inc. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in value stocks of small-cap companies having market capitalization less than that of the company with the largest capitalization included in the Russell 2000 Value Index. The fund employs fundamental analysis by focusing on factors such as discounted price-to-earnings (P/E) and price-to-cash flow (P/CF) multiples, strong balance sheets, and have experienced management to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Value Index. Bragg Capital Trust - Queens Road Small Cap Value Fund was formed in June 13, 2002 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


1031 South Caldwell StreetSuite 200Charlotte, NC 28203United StatesFounded in 2002



Phone: 704-377-0261

Fax: 704-334-9754

www.queensroadfunds.com/qrsvx.html







