After-tax 
returns are calculated using the highest historical individual federal marginal 
income tax rate and do not reflect the impact of state and local taxes. Actual 
after-tax returns depend on a shareholder’s tax situation and may differ from 
those shown. The after-tax returns are not relevant if you hold your Fund shares 
